Installing software on Ubuntu:

Install .tar files:
	tar xvfz file.tar.gz
	./configure
	make
	sudo make install

Make shift+numpad like MS Windows
	/etc/default/keyboard
	Change this XKBOPTIONS to XKBOPTIONS="numpad:microsoft"

ipconfig in Linux
	"ifconfig"

Opening as admin in Linux
	sudo gedit /path_to_file/

Create file in root directory
	sudo touch /file_path/
Create directory in root
	sudo mkdir /foler_path_name/

Installing ibus unikey
	sudo apt-get install ibus-unikey
	ibus restart
	Goto text entry then adding viet

