Install Xampp
    Create shortcut:
    https://www.panduboys.com/tips-tricks/xampp-control-panel-create-shortcut-in-ubuntu/
    
Shorten the terminal with:
		Open .bashrc
			PS1='\[\033[01;32m\]${C9_USER}\[\033[00m\]:\[\033[01;31m\]$\[\033[00m\] '
		Guide -> https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/how-to-customize-your-bash-prompt-on-a-linux-vps

		backup:
			PS1='${debian_chroot:+($debian_chroot)}\[\033[01;32m\]\u@\h\[\033[00m\]:\[\033[01;34m\]\w\[\033[00m\]\$ '
			
Installing MySQL-server
    https://www.digitalocean.com/community/tutorials/how-to-install-mysql-on-ubuntu-14-04
        
    service mysql start
    service mysql stop
    
    Config socket mysql with Rails:
        mysqladmin variables | grep socket
        
Installing Documentation for Programming: sudo apt-get install zeal

Installing qpdfview for linux: 
    sudo add-apt-repository ppa:b-eltzner/qpdfview
    sudo apt-get update
    sudo apt-get install qpdfview
    
